          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>Baltimore</placeName>
                                        <date>25 January 1849</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>Dear Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">On leaving <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName> for
                                        this place my father requested<lb/> me on my arrival here to
                                        address you a few lines for the purpose of
                                                  <sic>enquiring</sic><lb/> of you whether the
                                        article he forwarded you on the “Union of the
                                        Congregations<lb/> of the Jews in these States” will find a
                                        place in the Occident for <date>February</date><lb/> and if
                                        not in that number, whether it will appear in the
                                                  <date>March</date> one. I shall<lb/> feel thankful
                                        if you would drop a line in reply to this directed to me at the<lb/>
                                        <placeName>Baltimore</placeName> Post Office. In about a
                                        week from this I shall be in your<lb/> city when I shall
                                        have the pleasure of handing you a letter of
                                        introduction<lb/> from my father</p>
                              <p rend="indent(9)">I have the honor dear Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(9)">to subscribe myself yours respectfully</p>
                              <p rend="indent(10)">
                                        <persName role="author">Fred. Lindo</persName>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName>371 Walnut Street</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">
                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
                              </p>
